description: The Company operates in the field of specialized industrial construction and provides repair services for industrial chimneys and fireplaces and other altitute services. Additional funding is needed to participate in new private and public tenders. The Purchaser is one of the largest Lithuanian companies with revenue above EUR 4 billion.
The Company is a manufacturer of printer cartridges. The Purchaser is a wholesaler of printers and their equipment,  with revenue over EUR 100 million.
